      <title>摩根大通的Umunna说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-19/jpm-s-umunna-deep-pool-of-capital-for-sustainability-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通（JPMorgan Chase）可持续解决方案和EMEA绿色经济投资银行业务负责人Chuka Umunna表示，很少有投资者准备为可持续性“牺牲体面的回报”。他补充说，尽管较高的利率，供应链问题和公共政策差距的逆风，“我们在这个领域中完成了交易。”  （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-19/jpm-s-umunna-deep-pool-of-capital-for-sustainability-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 08:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
