    <item>
      <title>随着埃尔多安（Erdogan）加深净化，土耳其市场最为沉没</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/turkey-assets-sink-as-arrest-of-erdogan-rival-ups-political-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的里拉（Lira）沉没了，股票抛售引发了交易的停顿，政府债券收益率今年升至最高水平，因为投资者在将重要竞争对手逮捕给总统雷切普·泰伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）后抛弃了该国资产，这引起了政治风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/turkey-assets-sink-as-arrest-of-erdogan-rival-ups-political-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 06:58:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元总督Ueda讲话时，日元对美元的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/yen-slightly-weaker-against-dollar-after-boj-holds-rates-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元对美元造成的损失是因为日本银行州长Kazuo Ueda的评论在周三中央银行保持不变后，以进一步的税率上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/yen-slightly-weaker-against-dollar-after-boj-holds-rates-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>饲料前将股票静音；土耳其资产暴跌：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周三晚些时候，美国和欧洲股票期货在美联储的政策决定之前，在谨慎的贸易中发表了小小的举动。在当局拘留总统雷切普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）最杰出的竞争对手之后，土耳其的里拉（Lira）跌至创纪录的低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 22:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非阿克莱尔默塔尔（Arcelormittal）靠近资金交易，以节省工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/arcelormittal-south-africa-near-funding-deal-for-stricken-mills</link>
